trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for the design-time functionality of a Web Forms page and allows access to and manipulation of components and controls that are contained within the Web Forms page at design time.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma classe base para a funcionalidade de tempo de design de uma página de Web Forms e permite o acesso e manipulação de componentes e controles que estão contidos dentro da página de Web Forms em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: A design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], must provide its own derived version of the WebFormsRootDesigner class to control designers through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A> property of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Um design de host, tais como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], deve fornecer sua própria versão derivada da classe WebFormsRootDesigner para designers de controle por meio de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A>propriedade do designer.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A>

trans-unit.source: Control designers use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A> property to access and manipulate the containing Web Forms page at design time.
trans-unit.target: Controla o uso de designers de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A>propriedade para acessar e manipular o conteúdo da página Web Forms em tempo de design.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.RootDesigner%2A>
